		<page id="pg0">
			<p bold="true" italics="true">The UnderEnd</p>
			<p>Maybe you noticed that to get into space, you are missing some End-Ores. Well the End is a moon orbiting 4th planet of the Alpha Star so no, you cannot go there yet. But you can go to the UnderEnd. That is an End-like dimension deep under the surface of your world.</p>
			<link ref="ch2:d3">Portals</link>
		</page>
		<page>
			<p>Hint: You can get endstone for the portal in deeper layers of a Roguelike Dungeon.</p>
			<p>Available resources: Abyssum, Palladium, Duranite, Draconium and Prosperity Ore.</p>
